               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-232vc)&#xD; I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra-42rc)&#xD; I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     43ra-77vc)&#xD; I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 78ra-113vc)&#xD; I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     114ra-158vc)&#xD; I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 159ra-201rc)&#xD; I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     202ra-232vc), incomplete&#xD; &#xD; The commemorative notices are followed by
                     ʿarke-hymns.</summary>
