                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is incomplete, the end is missing. The
                           front and back boards are missing. &#xD; The sewing has been repaired;
                           some fols., especially in quire I, are held in place by crude recent
                           stitches.&#xD; The Ms. is severely worn at the margin, esp. at the
                           beginning and the end, sometimes with the loss of text (e.g., <locus target="#232rb">232rb</locus>).&#xD; Most fols. are affected by
                           humidity; several fols are stained with wax or dirt. The text has been
                           partly damaged on <locus target="#188v">188v</locus>, 221r.&#xD; f. 7 is
                           misplaced: it originally followed <locus target="#227">227</locus>. Some
                           fols. are missing.&#xD; <locus target="#42">42</locus> is half the size
                           of the other fols.&#xD; Holes or tears amended, e.g., on fols. 3, 17, 26,
